                <div class="col-lg-7 col-sm-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Complete your profile</h2>
                    <p class="slide-text-content">
                       If you're really excited to be one of our first Citizen Debate users, you can boost your ranking on the wait list simply by completing your full profile, which includes selecting an avatar and sharing a brief bio. By completing your profile, you'll earn 10 <a href="#thirdSection" class="inline-link">reputation points</a>.
                    </p>
                    <h2><a href="/profiles/new" class="btn btn-default btn-large">Setup profile</a></h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
  </section>

  <section class="vertical-scrolling">
        <div class="container">
