                    <h3>Reputation points reward you for your civility and active engagement with the community.</h3>
                    <p class="slide-text-content">
                      Earning reputation points helps you "climb the ladder" and secure your spot as one of the first Citizen Debaters.
                      <ul>
                        <li> Complete your profile: 10 reputation points </li>
