                        <li> Invite up to 5 friends: 15 reputation points </li>
                      </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-6">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="https://media2.giphy.com/media/13UKMgwNHrBSIo/200.gif" alt="">
